Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Soft-shelled turtle, soft-shelled \Nturtle, soft-shelled turtle-le! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Mentally and physically, \Ncompletely naked! ♪
