Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Mentally and physically, comp-- ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:06.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with the next \Nepisode of {\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui-{\i1}chan{\i0} here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always think that before summer starts,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have all sorts of expectations and \Nit gets you really excited and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.12,0:23:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but before you know it, it's \Nover without you doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true that there's not \Nmany special things going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, I can't think \Nthat a relationship with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you met in such an irresponsible \Ntime period would last long at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.97,0:23:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, both of us still have time, \Nso we should each do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that one is hard to reply to...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ways to Spend Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking!
